  "description": "Salt Provision Locker serves as a sealed storage compartment opening off Basaltwind Saltway, built into the ship’s dark, salt-scoured hull. Corrosion-tolerant shelving and lidded bins line the bulkheads, their edges chamfered to shed grit and preserve watertight seals. The floor consists of flush plates with recessed tie-down points for securing casks and canisters against Brineshade’s tidal stresses. Thick-glass service lamps cast a hard, pale light that renders the room’s austere fittings in sharp relief.",
